description:
On today’s show, Dr. Emily is joined by board certified OBGYN, medical director of VSPot Medi Spa, & author Dr. Carolyn Delucia to talk about the latest technological solutions for women’s health. 

The two of them talk about new, easy procedures that help women strengthen the pelvic floor & alleviate their pain, what vaginismus is, & her new book Ultimate Intimacy: The Revolutionary Science of Female Sexual Health. 


Follow Emily on all social: @sexwithemily

For even more sex talk, tips, & tricks visit sexwithemily.com

For more info on Dr. Carolyn Delucia, click HERE.
